text: Ivalente Kamuki is a 1989 Indian Malayalam film, directed by KS Sivachandran, starring Ashokan and Uma Maheswari in the lead roles. ==Cast== * Uma Maheswari * Hareesh * Varkala Madhu * Ashokan * Prathapachandran * Vijayan * Bobby Kottarakkara * Disco Shanthi * Kamala Kamesh * Ramu * Vincent * Jayalalitha ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 films Category:Indian films Category:1980s Malayalam-language films
